* Make `maruku` and `wikicloth` optional dependencies.
* Make `wikicloth` PKGBUILD available on the AUR to satisfy dependencies.
* YAML head matter for pages, ala Jekyll
* Nested site structure like :category/:page/ (where page is a markup file or a
  directory containing representable files)
* Automatic file representation (ala ARKWEB1 & ARKWEB2)
